user_prompt_template:
Life event: {life_event}
Audience: {audience}
Tone: {tone}
Context: {context}

Design a named operational system for this life event. Return ONLY valid JSON matching the schema below — no markdown, no prose.

Required schema:
{{
  "system_name": "string — a specific, named system (e.g. 'Estate Command System', 'Caregiver Operations Protocol')",
  "life_event": "string — the life event as provided",
  "operating_premise": "string — one sentence describing the core operational challenge",
  "system_objective": "string — the single measurable outcome this system achieves",
  "control_domains": [
    {{
      "name": "string — domain name",
      "purpose": "string — what this domain controls",
      "scope": "string — what is in and out of scope"
    }}
  ],
  "key_roles": [
    {{
      "role": "string",
      "responsibility": "string"
    }}
  ],
  "success_criteria": ["string"],
  "operating_constraints": ["string"]
}}
